Life lessons a culture clash and the values I inherited from my birthplace on my journey for a better community…I am thankful I met mama…for in every step I take I incorporate your sound teachings…life happens to the living…but with lungs to breathe, a beating heart and feed them proper, blood to move them…nothing can stop you from becoming a powerhouse for both your ancestors and descendants…you hold the key…and the world is at your footsteps…hold on to the depth of your sorrows, dreams and keep your faith in a growing future…one foot in front of each, feet on the ground, head in the clouds and above all never let anyone stop you from becoming your future…call it what you will, but it’s all about the willpower!!
